text: Alfred Johansson (8 May 1876 - 28 March 1941) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1941 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
